    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. It offers a smooth, comfortable ride and looks great both inside and out, making it the perfect choice for someone looking for a dependable and attractive car that's ready for its next adventure!",
